<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Lovey Details | Mobile Car Detailing</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --sage: #8aab8a;
    --sage-light: #b5c9b5;
    --sage-dark: #5e7d5e;
    --cream: #faf7f2;
    --warm-white: #f5f1ea;
    --black: #1a1a1a;
    --charcoal: #333;
    --muted: #777;
    --accent: #c8a96e;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--black);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.2);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sage-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--black); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none; color: var(--charcoal);
    font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--sage-dark); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--sage-dark);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 0.55rem 1.3rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--sage) !important; color: white !important; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    padding: 0 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 70% 50%, rgba(138,171,138,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 20% 80%, rgba(200,169,110,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .hero-dots {
    position: absolute; top: 15%; right: 8%;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(138,171,138,0.3) 1.5px, transparent 1.5px);
    background-size: 18px 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .hero-content {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(138,171,138,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.4);
    color: var(--sage-dark);
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }
  .hero-tag::before { content: '●'; font-size: 0.5rem; }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--sage-dark);
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.7; max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--black); color: var(--cream);
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: transparent; color: var(--black);
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem; border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--sage-dark); color: var(--sage-dark); }
  .hero-card {
    position: absolute; right: 5%; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: clamp(280px, 38vw, 480px);
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 0 0 0 1px rgba(138,171,138,0.2);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .hero-card-img {
    flex: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8aab8a 0%, #5e7d5e 40%, #3d5c3d 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 5rem; user-select: none;
  }
  .hero-card-label {
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--warm-white);
  }
  .hero-card-label p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
  .hero-card-label strong { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--black); }
  .hero-stat {
    position: absolute; left: -15px; bottom: 20%;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1rem 1.3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-stat .num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--sage-dark);
  }
  .hero-stat .lbl { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* SECTION COMMONS */
  section { padding: 6rem 2.5rem; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: ''; display: block;
    width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--sage-light);
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.75; max-width: 560px; font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services { background: var(--warm-white); }
  .services-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .services-head { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.2);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .service-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    background: var(--sage);
    transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .service-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .service-icon {
    font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .service-price {
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--sage-dark);
    font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .service-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .service-list {
    list-style: none; margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }
  .service-list li {
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .service-list li::before {
    content: '✓'; color: var(--sage-dark); font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
  .service-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--sage-dark);
    color: var(--sage-dark);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .service-btn:hover { background: var(--sage-dark); color: white; }

  /* BEFORE/AFTER */
  .gallery { background: var(--cream); }
  .gallery-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .gallery-head { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ba-card {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    background: white;
  }
  .ba-imgs {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    height: 200px;
  }
  .ba-img {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3rem; position: relative;
  }
  .ba-img.before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c4b9a8, #a09080); }
  .ba-img.after { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8aab8a, #5e7d5e); }
  .ba-label-overlay {
    position: absolute; bottom: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55); color: white;
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .ba-card-body { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
  .ba-card-body h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .ba-card-body p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); }

  /* WHY ME */
  .why { background: var(--sage-dark); color: white; }
  .why-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center; }
  .why .section-label { color: var(--sage-light); }
  .why .section-label::after { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
  .why h2 { color: white; }
  .why .section-intro { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  .why-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.2rem;
  }
  .why-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .why-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); }
  .why-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .why-item h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; color: white; }
  .why-item p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.6; }



  /* BOOKING */
  .booking {
    background: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .booking-inner { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .booking .section-label { justify-content: center; }
  .booking .section-label::after { display: none; }
  .booking h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .booking .section-intro { margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .booking-form {
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    border: 1px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .form-group label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--charcoal); }
  .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.3);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--black);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus, .form-group textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--sage-dark);
  }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 90px; }
  .form-full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  .form-submit {
    width: 100%; margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--black); color: var(--cream);
    border: none; border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--sage-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .booking-or {
    text-align: center; color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 1.5rem 0;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .booking-or::before, .booking-or::after {
    content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .dm-btn {
    display: block; text-align: center;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--black); color: var(--black);
    border-radius: 100px; padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .dm-btn:hover { background: var(--black); color: var(--cream); }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq { background: var(--warm-white); }
  .faq-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-head { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138,171,138,0.25);
    padding: 1.4rem 0;
  }
  .faq-q {
    font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--black); cursor: pointer;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem; list-style: none; user-select: none;
  }
  .faq-q::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-arrow {
    color: var(--sage-dark); font-size: 1.2rem;
    transition: transform 0.25s; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  details[open] .faq-arrow { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-a {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.75; padding-top: 0.8rem; font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--black); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: white; font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .footer-logo span { color: var(--sage-light); }
  footer p { font-size: 0.82rem; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .footer-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--sage-light); }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-card { display: none; }
    .why-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.2rem; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 4rem 1.2rem; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .hero-content > * {
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both;
  }
  .hero-tag { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .hero-content h1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .hero-sub { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .hero-btns { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Lovey<span>Details</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
    <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
    <li><a href="#booking" class="nav-cta">Book Now</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-dots"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Mobile Detailing · College Park, MD</div>
    <h1>Clean Car.<br><em>Better Vibes.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">You drive it. I revive it. Mobile car detailing that comes to you — affordable, thorough, and done right. Interior details, deep cleans, and full details available.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#booking" class="btn-primary">Book Now</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn-secondary">View Pricing →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-card">
    <div class="hero-card-img">🚗</div>
    <div class="hero-card-label">
      <p>Latest transformation</p>
      <strong>2019 Honda Civic — Full Detail</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="num">100%</div>
      <div class="lbl">Satisfaction</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="services-inner">
    <div class="services-head">
      <div class="section-label">What I Offer</div>
      <h2>Packages for Every Need</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Simple, transparent pricing. I come to you — no driving to a shop, no waiting around.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🧹</div>
        <h3>Basic Interior</h3>
        <div class="service-price">Starting at $60</div>
        <p class="service-desc">A thorough clean for everyday maintenance. Perfect if your car just needs some TLC.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Vacuum floors, seats & trunk</li>
          <li>Wipe down dashboard & console</li>
          <li>Clean cup holders & door pockets</li>
          <li>Window cleaning (interior)</li>
          <li>Air freshener finish</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#booking" class="service-btn">Book This →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">✨</div>
        <h3>Deep Interior</h3>
        <div class="service-price">Starting at $110</div>
        <p class="service-desc">For the cars that have been through it. Stains, pet hair, mystery smells — handled.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Everything in Basic</li>
          <li>Carpet & seat stain treatment</li>
          <li>Pet hair removal</li>
          <li>Leather/vinyl conditioning</li>
          <li>Detailed crevice cleaning</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#booking" class="service-btn">Book This →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🌟</div>
        <h3>Full Detail</h3>
        <div class="service-price">Starting at $140</div>
        <p class="service-desc">Interior AND exterior. The full glow-up. Walk out feeling like you just drove off the lot.</p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Everything in Deep Interior</li>
          <li>Hand wash & dry exterior</li>
          <li>Tire & rim clean</li>
          <li>Exterior wipe-down & shine</li>
          <li>Window clean inside & out</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#booking" class="service-btn">Book This →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GALLERY -->
<section class="gallery" id="gallery">
  <div class="gallery-inner">
    <div class="gallery-head">
      <div class="section-label">Transformations</div>
      <h2>Before & After</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">The results speak for themselves. These are real cars, real cleans.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="ba-card">
        <div class="ba-imgs">
          <div class="ba-img before">☕<span class="ba-label-overlay">Before</span></div>
          <div class="ba-img after">✨<span class="ba-label-overlay">After</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-card-body">
          <h4>Carpet Stain Removal</h4>
          <p>Deep Interior · 2021 Toyota Corolla</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-card">
        <div class="ba-imgs">
          <div class="ba-img before">🐾<span class="ba-label-overlay">Before</span></div>
          <div class="ba-img after">🪑<span class="ba-label-overlay">After</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-card-body">
          <h4>Pet Hair Deep Clean</h4>
          <p>Deep Interior · 2018 Ford Escape</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-card">
        <div class="ba-imgs">
          <div class="ba-img before">😬<span class="ba-label-overlay">Before</span></div>
