<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="faq-inner">
    <div class="faq-head">
      <div class="section-label">Questions</div>
      <h2>FAQ</h2>
    </div>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">Do you come to me? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">Yes! That's the whole point. I bring everything I need to your location: home, work, apartment parking lot, wherever. You don't have to go anywhere.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">How long does it take? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">Basic Interior: 1 to 1.5 hours. Deep Interior: 2 to 3 hours. Full Detail: 3 to 4 hours. Timing can vary based on how dirty the car is. I'd rather do it right than rush.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">Do I need to provide water or electricity? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">Nope! I bring my own supplies and equipment. All I need is access to your car and a little bit of space to work around it.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">Is there an extra fee for really dirty cars? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">If your car is exceptionally dirty (heavy pet hair, bad stains, a lot of clutter), there may be a small extra fee. I'll always let you know upfront before I start. No surprise charges.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">What payment methods do you accept? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">Cash, Venmo, Cash App, and Zelle all work. Payment is due at the end of your appointment once you've seen the results and you're happy.</p>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-q">Do you service all car types? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span></summary>
      <p class="faq-a">Cars, SUVs, and small trucks, yes! For larger vehicles like full-size vans or pickup trucks, pricing may be slightly higher. Just mention it when you book.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

